    This iterator wraps a DistributableQueryFilter which is deserialized from a byte array passed as an option with a "filter" key. Also, the model is needed to deserialize the row into a set of fields that can be used by the filter. The model is deserialized from a byte array stored as an option with the key "model". If either one of these serialized options are not successfully found, this iterator will accept everything.
